config BR2_PACKAGE_RASPUTIN_AGENT
	bool "rasputin-agent"
	default y
	help
	  The Rasputin node agent. Runs on every Rasputin node; dials the
	  control-plane NATS broker outbound (never listens), reports
	  inventory + heartbeat, and executes commands (reboot, metrics,
	  docker, bmc, mesh enroll).

	  Installed from a pre-built, statically-linked release binary
	  published by the rasputin-control-plane repo's CI — see
	  package/rasputin-agent/rasputin-agent.mk and the design doc
	  os-images/buildroot-os.md §5.

	  https://github.com/geekdojo/rasputin-control-plane
